==Career== Lejeune began his career in 1998 with [[Toulouse Fontaines Club]]<ref>[http://www.footmercato.net/qui-pour-relancer-un-espoir_article41121.html Qui pour relancer un espoir tricolore en perdition ?]</ref> before moving to [[AJ Auxerre|Auxerre]] in July 2000,<ref>[http://www.mercato365.com/infos-clubs/auxerre/article_310359_auxerre-kevin-lejeune-Mes-qualites-sont-toujours-la-.shtml Â«Mes qualitÃ©s sont toujours lÃ Â» le 12 avril 2009]</ref> making his league debut six years later on 19 November 2006 during a 1&ndash;0 win over [[Toulouse FC|Toulouse]]. On 6 January 2009, he joined [[FC Nantes]] on loan for the remainder of the 2009&ndash;10 season.<ref>[http://www.fcnantes.com/articles/article2809.php?num=2714 Kevin Lejeune rejoint le FC Nantes]</ref> In July 2010, he joined [[Cardiff City F.C.|Cardiff City]] on trial, playing 45 minutes of a pre-season 3&ndash;0 defeat to [[Portimonense S.C.|Portimonense]].<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/footballnation/football-news/2010/07/20/frenchman-leroux-is-city-s-mystery-new-player-91466-26886842/ |title=Frenchman Lejeune is Cardiff's mystery new player |publisher=[[South Wales Echo]] |date=2010-06-20 |accessdate=2010-08-09}}</ref>
